reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Compact size. Great for what I was looking for.
reviews.reviewText: Does its thing very well. Hanged mine from the front of the head rest on the passenger seat (‘23 Colorado) since I seldom have any riders -other than two dogs that ride in the back. Attaches/detaches easily with the adjustable strap and buckle. Nice self closing diaphragm on top to insert trash. Inside plastic membrane looks to be sealed for ease of cleaning and waterproofing. Velcro closure on top. Nice mesh storage on front and two sides. One clip on each side to attach a plastic bag if wanted to use with it. Good price, would recommend and buy again.

reviews.reviewText: It's cute and it's practical, my favorite combination when purchasing a product.
